Really, it does stop us short on our weapon skills, but with SC and other drops, we can get our weapon skill to 50 from 39 to flatten out our variance.  Yes, we wouldn't be able to use the 2 highest weapon styles, but that's an option for us, something we Skalds (46,44,17) just don't seem to have.<br>
